{
  "stem": "17299.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 342.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In May-- must be around the 20s, I fainted due to malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day, they put me on a truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because each time a group of sick ones were in a camp, they were taken out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now this is the worst part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the first transport, they were taken out by bus.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We feel they come in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they did not come in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were laid out in front of the bus, shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The second transport, there was-- one fellow was taken by-- the father was taken by his son or somebody else towards the truck.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And an SS NCO named [NON-ENGLISH], who was the commandant for Jungfernhof, walked up to him and said, he is too sick, and put a bullet in his head, in my presence.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he gave the orders that all jackets and shoes to be removed from those who are going on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the temperature must have been between 20 or 30 below 0.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were under no illusions about what's happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the third transport had to go out, people were fighting it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the camp administration put them on the trucks anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not one of those between January, February and March and April came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They all were shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because later on, the clothing came back in the depot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first transport to come in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were only 12 on that truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were brought in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Usually, there are 50 or 60 taken out who are sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first person I ran into was my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
